l-uqubah","tag-laziness-sloth-al-kasl","tag-unbelief-kufr","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3G3","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":13906,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/02\/fajr-protection-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14139,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Whoever prays Fajr prayer under protection of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jundab ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever\u00a0performs the dawn prayer will be under the guardianship of Allah. Thus, let not one of you be held to account for his guardianship in any way. For if Allah seeks recompense for his guardianship\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15805,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/friday-jumuah-heedless\/","url_meta":{"origin":14139,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Neglecting Friday prayer leads to hard heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said while upon his wooden pulpit, \u201cPeople need to stop neglecting the Friday prayers, lest Allah place a seal over their hearts and then they become heedless.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 865 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19591,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/al-ala-ghashiyah-jumuah-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":14139,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Surat al-A&#8217;la and al-Ghashiyah in Eid, Friday prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Num\u2019an ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would recite in the two Eid prayers and in the Friday prayer the chapters, \u201cGlorify the name of your Lord the Most High,\u201d (87:1) and, \u201cHas there come to you the news of the overwhelming?\u201d (88:1).\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28121,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/ten-rakaat-sunan\/","url_meta":{"origin":14139,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary Sunan prayers throughout day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, two prostrations before and after noon prayer, two prostrations after sunset prayer, two prostrations after evening prayer, and two prostrations after Friday prayer. As for sunset and evening prayer, they were in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41207,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/missing-salat-al-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":14139,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Warning against missing congregational \u2018Asr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever misses the afternoon prayer, it is as if he had lost his family and his property.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 552, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 626 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/mindful-friday-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14139,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jumu\u2019ah: Have presence at sermon, be near to Imam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah ibn Jundub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe present at the sermon and come close to the Imam. Verily, a man continues to distance himself until he is delayed from Paradise, even though he will eventually enter it.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"s